  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Prepare a 6-ounce ramekin by greasing it with butter or cooking spray.",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together almond flour, onion powder, garlic powder, salt, and pepper.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together eggs, grated cheddar, and Marmite.",
    "Add the dry ingredients to the wet ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Pour the mixture into the prepared ramekin and smooth the top.",
    "Dot the top of the ramekin with butter pieces.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes or until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
